      <h1>Online Aptitude test Help</h1>  

      <h3><u><font color = "maroon">Rules & Regulations</font></u></h3>
<font color = "maroon">
 <ol>
 <li>Students with IT background can appear for the exam, to test his knowledge in the sphere of IT.
 <li>Students have to Register with the system to get his/her Test ID, using with which he/she can appear for the exam.
 <li>Once Test ID is issued a student can start exam by clicking start exam link in the home page.
 <li>You can take a trial test before taking a real test to get accustomed with the system.
 <li>You have four levels of test to answer. You can go for higher level only after appearing for the lower level.
 <li>You will have to attend number of questions for each level you select for the test.
 <li>There is a time limit within which you have to complete answering all the questions.
 <li>You will have four answer for each question, you have to select any one from the choices.
 <li>Once you finish answering all the questions or exceeded the time limit you will see the overall performance of the test in the results page.
 <li>Your results are stored in the database, you can see later at any time.
 <li>Best of  Luck.
</ol>
